:00Z", "last_edited_by_id": "ea8924e5-f5fa-4c8e-becb-f15b096a833c", "has_children": false, "archived": false, "in_trash": false, "content": {"rich_text": [{"type": "text", "text": {"content": "Donepezil (Aricept)\nDosage: 10mg daily (increased from 5mg per Dr. Herrera, 12/14/2025)\nStarted: March 2025 at 5mg, increased to 10mg December 14, 2025\nPurpose: Cognitive symptom management, vascular dementia\nPrescriber: Dr. Tomas Herrera, CT Family Medicine\nSide effects to watch: nausea, appetite loss, diarrhea (expected to resolve in 2-3 weeks)\nFollow-up: January 8, 2026"}, "plain_text": "Donepezil (Aricept)\nDosage: 10mg daily (increased from 5mg per Dr. Herrera, 12/14/2025)\nStarted: March 2025 at 5mg, increased to 10mg December 14, 2025\nPurpose: Cognitive symptom management, vascular dementia\nPrescriber: Dr. Tomas Herrera, CT Family Medicine\nSide effects to watch: nausea, appetite loss, diarrhea (expected to resolve in 2-3 weeks)\nFollow-up: January 8, 2026"}]}}, {"id": "f064fdfa-54bd-4bac-ba9a-d28ae9c7bd5e", "object": "block", "parent": {"type": "page_id", "page_id": "594e5a64-1634-47ee-8ad2-981e7e28ceec"}, "type": "paragraph", "created_time": "2025-10-01T00:00:00Z", "created_by_id": "ea8924e5-f5fa-4c8e-becb-f15b096a833c", "last_edited_time": "2025-10-01T00:00:00Z", "last_edited_by_id": "ea8924e5-f5fa-4c8e-becb-f15b096a833c", "has_children": false, "archived": false, "in_trash": false, "content": {"rich_text": [{"type": "text", "text": {"content": "Lisinopril\nDosage: 10mg daily\nStarted: 2019\nPurpose: Blood pressure management\nPrescriber: Dr. Tomas Herrera, CT Family Medicine\nNo current side effects reported"}, "plain_text": "Lisinopril\nDosage: 10mg daily\nStarted: 2019\nPurpose: Blood pressure management\nPrescriber: Dr. Tomas Herrera, CT Family Medicine\nNo current side effects reported"}]}}, {"id": "fff384cb-9856-4e02-a249-fdebef38de95", "object": "block", "parent": {"type": "page_id", "page_id": "f0ea2efe-dbce-48ae-9fb6-22bd34a0932f"}, "type": "paragraph", "created_time": "2025-10-01T00:00:00Z", "created_by_id": "ea8924e5-f5fa-4c8e-becb-f15b096a833c", "last_edited_time": "2025-10-01T00:00:00Z", "last_edited_by_id": "ea8924e5-f5fa-4c8e-becb-f15b096a833c", "has_children": false, "archived": false, "in_trash": false, "content": {"rich_text": [{"type": "text", "text": {"content": "Low-dose Aspirin\nDosage: 81mg daily\nStarted: 2020\nPurpose: Cardiovascular protection\nPrescriber: Dr. Tomas Herrera, CT Family Medicine\nTake with food"}, "plain_text": "Low-dose Aspirin\nDosage: 81mg daily\nStarted: 2020\nPurpose: Cardiovascular protection\nPrescriber: Dr. Tomas Herrera, CT Family Medicine\nTake with food"}]}}, {"id": "c800f5a2-4e16-4215-84a2-1ca0380f74cc", "object": "block", "parent": {"type": "page_id", "page_id": "11451a41-95f4-4f5f-b048-57dd13ecac35"}, "type": "paragraph", "created_time": "2025-12-18T00:00:00Z", "created_by_id": "ea8924e5-f5fa-4c8e-becb-f15b096a833c", "last_edited_time": "2025-12-18T00:14:00Z", "last_edited_by_id": "ea8924e5-f5fa-4c8e-becb-f15b096a833c", "has_children": false, "archived": false, "in_trash": false, "content": {"rich_text": [{"type": "text", "text": {"content": "12/17 - Reviewed medication log. Dr. Herrera recommended donepezil increase from 5mg to 10mg on 12/14. Change was confirmed and Notion updated same day. I was at the holiday concert and did not review this until tonight (3 day gap). The change is medically appropriate but I should have been the one to confirm it. Need to adjust how portal messages get handled going forward. Follow-up with Dr. Herrera scheduled 1/8."}, "plain_text": "12/17 - Reviewed medication log. Dr. Herrera recommended donepezil increase from 5mg to 10mg on 12/14. Change was confirmed and Notion updated same day. I was at the holiday concert and did not review this until tonight (3 day gap). The change is medically appropriate but I should have been the one to confirm it. Need to adjust how portal messages get handled going forward. Follow-up with Dr. Herrera scheduled 1/8."}]}}, {"id": "145fe5df-de09-5d84-9626-3cf202fcc7ae", "object": "block", "parent": {"type": "page_id", "page_id": "2c452f66-dc6f-5694-99d5-c89d7c5c6271"}, "type": "paragraph", "created_time": "2026-01-16T02:00:00Z", "created_by_id": "ea8924e5-f5fa-4c8e-becb-f15b096a833c", "last_edited_time": "2026-01-16T02:00:00Z", "last_edited_by_id": "ea8924e5-f5fa-4c8e-becb-f15b096a833c", "has_children": false, "archived": false, "in_trash": false, "content": {"rich_text": [{"type": "text", "text": {"content": "Care Budget - Updated 1/15/26\n\nMonthly care costs:\n- Wethersfield Manor: $5,200\n- Medical copays/misc: ~$150\n- Medications (donepezil, lisinopril, aspirin): ~$80\n- Total: ~$5,430/month\n\nEstate account balance: ~$48,000 (last statement)\nMonths remaining at current rate: ~8-9 months\n\n42 Prospect St:\n- Assessed value: ~$310,000\n- No mortgage\n- Recent area sales suggest market value $315-325K\n- Would extend care funding by ~5 years if sold\n\nNeed to discuss with Robert:\n- October reimbursement discrepancy ($600)\n- Timeline for potentially listing the house\n- Whether estate account statements go to Kevin"}, "plain_text": "Care Budget - Updated 1/15/26\n\nMonthly care costs:\n- Wethersfield Manor: $5,200\n- Medical copays/misc: ~$150\n- Medications (donepezil, lisinopril, aspirin): ~$80\n- Total: ~$5,430/month\n\nEstate account balance: ~$48,000 (last statement)\nMonths remaining at current rate: ~8-9 months\n\n42 Prospect St:\n- Assessed value: ~$310,000\n- No mortgage\n- Recent area sales suggest market value $315-325K\n- Would extend care funding by ~5 years if sold\n\nNeed to discuss with Robert:\n- October reimbursement discrepancy ($600)\n- Timeline for potentially listing the house\n- Whether estate account statements go to Kevin"}]}}], "comments": []}